sequenceDiagram
    participant Browser as Browser<br/>(Data Scientist)
    participant Gateway as OpenShift Gateway<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant KRBP as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Backend as Fastify Backend<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant GenAiBFF as gen-ai BFF<br/>8143/TCP HTTPS
    participant MaasBFF as maas BFF<br/>8243/TCP HTTPS
    participant LlamaStack as LlamaStack<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant MaaSGW as MaaS Gateway<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over Browser,K8sAPI: Flow 1: User Request through Dashboard

    Browser->>Gateway: HTTPS/443<br/>Cookie/Bearer Token
    Gateway->>KRBP: HTTPS/8443<br/>TLS (serving cert)<br/>Bearer Token
    KRBP->>K8sAPI: SubjectAccessReview<br/>HTTPS/6443 TLS<br/>ServiceAccount
    K8sAPI-->>KRBP: Allowed
    KRBP->>Backend: HTTP/8080<br/>X-Auth-Request-User<br/>X-Auth-Request-Groups
    Backend->>K8sAPI: REST/WebSocket<br/>HTTPS/6443 TLS<br/>User's Bearer Token
    K8sAPI-->>Backend: K8s Resources
    Backend-->>KRBP: JSON Response
    KRBP-->>Gateway: HTTPS Response
    Gateway-->>Browser: HTTPS Response

    Note over Browser,MaaSGW: Flow 2: Federated Module BFF Request (sidecar mode)

    Browser->>Gateway: HTTPS/443<br/>Cookie/Bearer Token
    Gateway->>KRBP: HTTPS/8443<br/>Bearer Token
    KRBP->>K8sAPI: SubjectAccessReview
    K8sAPI-->>KRBP: Allowed
    KRBP->>Backend: HTTP/8080<br/>X-Auth-Request headers
    Backend->>GenAiBFF: HTTPS/8143<br/>TLS (serving cert)<br/>x-forwarded-access-token
    GenAiBFF->>LlamaStack: HTTPS/443<br/>TLS<br/>Bearer Token
    LlamaStack-->>GenAiBFF: Inference Result
    GenAiBFF-->>Backend: JSON Response
    Backend-->>KRBP: Response
    KRBP-->>Gateway: HTTPS Response
    Gateway-->>Browser: HTTPS Response

    Note over GenAiBFF,MaaSGW: Flow 3: Inter-BFF Communication (gen-ai to maas)

    GenAiBFF->>MaasBFF: HTTPS/8243<br/>TLS (serving cert)<br/>x-forwarded-access-token
    MaasBFF->>MaaSGW: HTTPS/443<br/>TLS<br/>Bearer Token
    MaaSGW-->>MaasBFF: MaaS Token
    MaasBFF-->>GenAiBFF: Token Response
